  • What is the price of Optimism today?

    Today, September 8, 2025, the price of Optimism (OP) is $0.75.

  • How do I add Optimism to MetaMask?

    MetaMask automatically displays popular tokens like OptimismOPwithin your wallet. If you are not seeing your OP in MetaMask, you can manually add it using the "Add to MetaMask" button above, over the price chart. Please remember that you first need to install MetaMask extension if you are on a PC or Mac (desktop computer).If you are on mobile, please check out our MetaMask Support guide here for more info.

  • How do I buy Optimism?

    Buying Optimism (OP) in MetaMask wallet is speedy, simple, and safe. You can buy Optimism (OP) tokens directly in MetaMask using payment methods like a credit card, debit card, bank account, Apple Pay, Google Pay, or PayPal. Theres no need for centralized exchanges. Select from thousands of your favorite tokens to buy on over 15 networks including Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, Linea, Base, and more.

  • How do I sell Optimism?

    MetaMask makes it easy to sell your Optimism (OP) and convert your crypto to cash. You can exchange from MetaMask wallet directly to your debit card, credit card, PayPal, or bank account. By removing unnecessary steps and cutting excess fees, offramping your digital assets is fast and simple.

  • How do I swap Optimism?

    Swapping OP is simple and cost-effective with MetaMask. Choose from thousands of your favorite tokens across ten networks including Ethereum, Solana, Linea, Base, and Arbitrum. MetaMask Swaps also include gas fees right in your quotes, making swapping crypto as smooth as can be.

  • How do I bridge Optimism?

    Bridging crypto across chains allows you to move tokens from one network to another. With MetaMask, bridging Optimism (OP) is easy, secure, and cost-effective. Our aggregator finds the most efficient routes to move your digital assets from one chain to another. And with cross-chain swapping, bridging and swapping can take place at the same time in a single transaction. Meaning: instead of bridging OP from chain A and wrapping or unwrapping it on chain B, you can swap OP from chain A to a second token on chain B, all in one move.

  • What is Optimism's all-time high?

  • What can you do with Optimism?

    With Optimism, you can send and receive OP, the networks native token, and use it to pay transaction fees on certain networks. OP is supported in decentralized apps for trading, staking, yield optimization, and payments. You can participate in DeFi protocols, bridge assets between networks, or use OP in select web3 financial strategies, all with Ethereum-compatible speed and flexibility.

  • What is the price history of Optimism?

  • How do I trade Optimism for other cryptocurrencies?

    Trading Optimism (OP) for ETH, WBTC, or SOL can be done directly in MetaMask. For more information on how to swap OP, head to MetaMask Support.
